♪ Smile ♪

56:35.960 --> 56:41.957
♪ Until you don't need
to control yourself ♪

56:43.720 --> 56:44.790
Okay, I'll go first.

56:44.840 --> 56:47.116
I'm Di.

56:47.160 --> 56:49.197
I am from Fort Collins,
Colorado.

56:49.240 --> 56:50.515
I'm 25 years old.

56:50.560 --> 56:52.358
Wink, wink.

56:52.400 --> 56:55.234
Um, I'm an Aries.
Favorite color is purple.

56:55.280 --> 56:58.114
